ActMarine Liability Act
PrecisAppointment of MARK A. M. GAUTHIER of Gatineau, Quebec, to be the Administrator of the Ship-source Oil Pollution Fund, on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year, or until such time as a new administrator is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective april 3, 2023.
